WEBVTT

01:31.700 --> 01:35.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:35.980 --> 01:38.980
[Episode 22]

01:49.790 --> 01:50.650
It's already dawn,

01:51.350 --> 01:52.540
and we've heard all the stories.

01:52.870 --> 01:54.100
Why aren't they out yet?

01:57.510 --> 01:58.570
They're driving me crazy.

02:00.120 --> 02:00.770
In fact,

02:02.590 --> 02:04.490
there is one other way to help Mu Long.

02:06.150 --> 02:06.660
Say it.

02:10.820 --> 02:12.040
The solution lies inside you.

02:14.040 --> 02:17.130
You mean the Dragon Deity's Power?

02:34.030 --> 02:34.690
That scent...

02:37.280 --> 02:38.220
Master Dragon Deity?

02:42.950 --> 02:44.220
Searing flames, ignite!

03:35.790 --> 03:36.940
You're not Lu Wuyi.

03:56.110 --> 03:56.690
Come with me.

03:57.830 --> 03:58.660
Master Dragon Deity?

04:01.070 --> 04:01.850
It's you?

04:06.070 --> 04:07.570
So you really are helping Lu Wuyi.

04:09.230 --> 04:09.730
Wuyi,

04:12.280 --> 04:12.940
what happened to you?

04:14.390 --> 04:14.940
Wu...

04:15.000 --> 04:15.540
It was him.

04:16.990 --> 04:18.780
He used Word Magic on Mu Long.

04:20.040 --> 04:21.610
He joined forces with Jiu Ying long ago.

04:22.870 --> 04:23.810
I found out,

04:25.310 --> 04:26.540
and when I tried to tell you, Wangyan,

04:27.790 --> 04:29.020
he wounded me.

04:31.840 --> 04:32.460
Ji Ling

04:33.350 --> 04:33.980
hurt you?

04:38.190 --> 04:38.850
Ji,

04:39.870 --> 04:40.580
help me.

04:41.550 --> 04:43.370
I'm afraid that if Wangyan learns the truth,

04:44.310 --> 04:45.140
she'll come to despise me.

04:46.430 --> 04:47.660
I don't want to lose her.

05:00.310 --> 05:01.220
You're not saying anything.

05:01.750 --> 05:02.810
Are you admitting it?

05:07.750 --> 05:09.100
Why did you give me this bracelet?

05:11.750 --> 05:13.170
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning

05:13.720 --> 05:14.900
can suppress evil.

05:17.190 --> 05:17.900
Wear it,

05:18.350 --> 05:19.460
and it can temporarily suppress

05:19.520 --> 05:20.490
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

05:26.080 --> 05:26.810
Is it really meant to suppress

05:26.840 --> 05:28.140
Jiu Ying's spirit fragment?

05:28.520 --> 05:29.610
That bracelet is fake.

05:32.110 --> 05:32.610
Ji Ling,

05:33.280 --> 05:34.340
didn't you say that bracelet

05:34.480 --> 05:35.100
could suppress

05:35.110 --> 05:36.050
Jiu Ying's fragment?

05:36.520 --> 05:37.540
Was it a lie?

05:39.480 --> 05:40.730
If I hadn't lied to him,

05:41.670 --> 05:43.580
how could I have lowered his guard?

05:45.480 --> 05:46.980
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

05:47.920 --> 05:49.490
You really did keep your promise.

05:50.750 --> 05:52.140
Now you can sit

05:53.110 --> 05:54.850
on the Dragon Deity's throne

05:55.840 --> 05:56.780
forever.

06:04.280 --> 06:05.250
I believe Wuyi.

06:07.160 --> 06:07.850
Wangyan...

06:08.640 --> 06:10.050
You've sat on the Dragon Deity's throne too long.

06:10.750 --> 06:11.730
You don't want to give it up,

06:11.990 --> 06:12.460
do you?

06:12.990 --> 06:14.780
As long as the Word Magic on Mu Long isn't lifted,

06:15.400 --> 06:17.020
Han Ba won't hand over the Dragon Deity's Power,

06:18.920 --> 06:20.340
and Wu Shiguang won't be able to become a dragon.

06:21.160 --> 06:22.220
And that means

06:23.350 --> 06:24.370
the throne stays his.

06:25.160 --> 06:27.370
You betrayed your oath to Master Chi Wen.

06:27.960 --> 06:29.410
Didn't you reclaim your demon power too,

06:30.670 --> 06:32.020
betraying your oath just the same?

06:32.600 --> 06:34.050
You have no right to accuse me.

06:36.160 --> 06:37.730
But why did he snatch Mu Long's pendant?

06:38.160 --> 06:39.100
Because Su Jian's memories

06:39.310 --> 06:40.340
are stored inside it.

06:40.920 --> 06:42.100
He wanted to help Jiu Ying

06:42.480 --> 06:43.980
hide something shameful.

06:46.080 --> 06:47.540
It has Jian's memories inside.

06:55.430 --> 06:56.460
Even if you take the pendant, it won't help.

06:56.840 --> 06:57.980
We already know everything.

06:58.600 --> 06:59.410
Lu Wuyi

07:00.600 --> 07:02.490
was created by Jiu Ying,

07:03.670 --> 07:04.220
wasn't she?

07:20.430 --> 07:21.580
It's empty?

07:22.310 --> 07:23.250
The memories are gone.

07:28.430 --> 07:29.250
You lied to me.

07:37.520 --> 07:38.220
So she

07:40.840 --> 07:42.370
took the memories back.

07:43.870 --> 07:44.460
The manuscript!

07:44.640 --> 07:45.780
The first chapter of that manuscript

07:46.190 --> 07:47.490
was Little Pomegranate's story.

07:47.790 --> 07:48.490
The handwriting

07:48.750 --> 07:49.980
was all crooked.

07:50.230 --> 07:51.250
It was really ugly.

07:51.640 --> 07:52.410
But still, I recognized

07:52.430 --> 07:53.370
the words "Little" and "Pomegranate."

07:53.370 --> 07:54.430
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]

07:54.430 --> 07:55.730
That was Su Jian's handwriting.

07:56.640 --> 07:57.930
She wrote the story

08:00.520 --> 08:01.460
of Little Pomegranate.

08:01.780 --> 08:06.900
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams...♪

08:11.520 --> 08:14.140
Master Dragon Deity returned this to us.

08:14.870 --> 08:15.660
He didn't want it.

08:18.100 --> 08:21.300
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

08:21.540 --> 08:23.540
♪I am only♪

08:23.660 --> 08:26.700
♪A murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

08:27.080 --> 08:28.220
I'll go bring the medicine over.

08:28.900 --> 08:34.180
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

08:35.540 --> 08:40.580
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

08:42.130 --> 08:45.300
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

08:45.460 --> 08:48.780
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness♪

08:48.980 --> 08:51.820
♪Watching the corner of your lips stained♪

08:51.900 --> 08:54.620
♪With a touch of dark crimson♪

08:56.220 --> 09:01.900
♪From now on, you'll never grow old♪

09:02.260 --> 09:07.460
♪Even with earth between us, I'll softly sing with you♪

09:09.540 --> 09:12.660
♪In spring, I'll gather a thousand flowers for you♪

09:12.980 --> 09:15.660
♪In winter, I'll boil snow to warm the fading dusk♪

09:16.380 --> 09:21.380
♪Of joy and sorrow, of countless softly lit homes, I'll speak to you♪

09:22.580 --> 09:28.980
♪Brewing the years into a daydream impossible to wake from♪

09:29.340 --> 09:35.940
♪Draining every joy and sorrow, crushing the void within the heart♪

09:36.620 --> 09:39.700
♪The white-haired one looks on through tear-blurred eyes♪

09:40.060 --> 09:44.260
♪Sighing for youth, when words defied the heart♪

09:44.820 --> 09:50.780
♪Whose dream lies buried beneath the cenotaph?♪

09:55.220 --> 09:59.700
♪Heavy snow falls, silver light shimmering through the world♪

10:01.260 --> 10:06.540
♪On the lake of the heart drifts a withered lotus leaf♪

10:06.540 --> 10:07.820
[Nian]

10:07.820 --> 10:10.980
♪A young man sits alone with his back turned♪

10:11.260 --> 10:14.420
♪Flowers bloom around the gravestone♪

10:14.660 --> 10:20.020
♪My beloved, I've grown old keeping watch over you♪

10:21.820 --> 10:27.620
♪From now on, you'll never be alone♪

10:28.020 --> 10:33.740
♪Even across the Bridge of Oblivion, I'll say it to you out loud...♪

10:34.310 --> 10:35.770
So what she wrote was "Nian,"

10:37.670 --> 10:39.370
as in never forgetting.

10:46.190 --> 10:47.700
So whenever the wind stirred the tree,

10:49.310 --> 10:50.650
all it carried

10:52.240 --> 10:53.220
were sighs.

10:55.670 --> 10:57.580
And yet I never had the courage to go up to her.

11:13.070 --> 11:13.610
Don't go.

11:14.000 --> 11:14.820
It's dangerous.

11:23.360 --> 11:24.420
His demon power is leaking out.

11:26.160 --> 11:28.060
To keep another drought from breaking out,

11:28.790 --> 11:30.370
I grant you the Dragon Deity's Power.

11:30.920 --> 11:32.180
It can temporarily stop

11:32.240 --> 11:33.490
your demonic energy from leaking.

11:34.640 --> 11:37.610
But this borrowed power will run out one day.

11:38.400 --> 11:38.940
Wangyan,

11:39.640 --> 11:40.980
Han Ba's mind is in chaos.

11:41.520 --> 11:42.820
He's about to lose control of his demon power.

11:46.430 --> 11:47.460
I won't be able

11:48.120 --> 11:49.530
to see Mu Long finish

11:49.590 --> 11:50.890
her story collection after all.

11:55.360 --> 11:56.730
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

11:58.430 --> 12:00.460
in the place where I first met Su Jian.

12:02.710 --> 12:03.980
I placed a seal on it.

12:05.000 --> 12:06.610
Only when Mu Long regains consciousness

12:07.400 --> 12:09.060
will it be unsealed.

12:10.880 --> 12:12.180
Please, save Mu Long for me.

12:16.920 --> 12:17.460
I'm sorry

12:18.310 --> 12:19.220
that even at the very end,

12:19.520 --> 12:21.340
I'm still this selfish.

12:25.180 --> 12:27.660
♪How pitiful, how sad...♪

12:32.120 --> 12:32.820
This is for you.

12:33.360 --> 12:34.300
At just over 20,

12:34.670 --> 12:36.650
you're the perfect age for carrying an old man's fan.

12:37.220 --> 12:40.300
♪Just lend me one more tomorrow♪

12:40.620 --> 12:43.460
♪To go back and see my hometown♪

12:43.820 --> 12:46.620
♪Holding all my bitter regrets♪

12:46.780 --> 12:49.500
♪As I drift farther away♪

12:50.020 --> 12:52.940
♪I won't wipe my tears dry♪

12:53.300 --> 12:56.100
♪Afraid the sorrow fades too light♪

12:59.820 --> 13:02.260
♪No more longing♪

13:04.780 --> 13:07.500
♪Forget me not, forget me not♪

13:07.820 --> 13:10.980
♪You and I made a promise♪

13:11.140 --> 13:13.580
♪They laugh at me for going mad♪

13:14.020 --> 13:16.820
♪So what if I have?♪

13:17.460 --> 13:20.420
♪Miss me not, miss me not...♪

13:21.470 --> 13:22.420
I'm coming...

13:24.710 --> 13:25.820
to you.

13:26.580 --> 13:30.460
♪It was never here♪

14:09.710 --> 14:11.460
Because of what you did,

14:12.160 --> 14:13.770
none of this can be undone now.

14:14.470 --> 14:16.100
The memories were long gone from that pendant.

14:16.550 --> 14:18.060
Whether I took it or not,

14:18.590 --> 14:19.850
nothing could have prevented

14:19.850 --> 14:21.940
Han Ba's collapse after learning the truth.

14:22.790 --> 14:24.010
The ending was written from the start.

14:24.670 --> 14:25.850
Blaming me won't change a thing.

14:27.590 --> 14:28.820
Such is fate.

14:30.790 --> 14:32.130
No matter how many times we try,

14:36.790 --> 14:38.180
some things can never be undone.

14:40.670 --> 14:41.490
Some people

14:42.310 --> 14:43.700
are destined to be like two great mountains

14:45.160 --> 14:46.490
separated by an endless plain,

14:47.360 --> 14:48.300
a canyon,

14:49.240 --> 14:51.220
or a distance they can never cross.

14:52.190 --> 14:53.580
They watch over each other from afar,

14:54.950 --> 14:57.220
yet can never take one step or even half a step

14:59.400 --> 15:00.130
toward one another.

15:01.950 --> 15:02.700
Tell me.

15:04.360 --> 15:05.100
Tell me.

15:07.310 --> 15:08.530
What are they waiting for?

15:10.190 --> 15:11.670
What are they waiting for?

15:13.760 --> 15:15.220
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:16.670 --> 15:17.940
They're waiting for a snowfall.

15:20.160 --> 15:21.420
With just one snowfall,

15:22.310 --> 15:23.890
they can bow to each other from afar

15:24.520 --> 15:25.580
and grow old together.

15:26.760 --> 15:28.180
With just one snowfall,

15:29.160 --> 15:30.980
they can bow to each other from afar

15:31.920 --> 15:33.220
and grow old together.

15:46.120 --> 15:46.610
What,

15:47.470 --> 15:48.180
you don't like it anymore?

15:50.120 --> 15:51.730
It doesn't really go with what I'm wearing today.

15:58.920 --> 15:59.580
Come with me!

16:03.000 --> 16:03.580
Wuyi!

16:10.790 --> 16:12.820
I wonder whether Wu Shiguang and Wangyan

16:13.430 --> 16:14.890
will be able to find Ji Ling and Wuyi.

16:16.470 --> 16:17.340
Right now, only Ji Ling

16:17.360 --> 16:18.220
can wake you.

16:19.310 --> 16:20.530
There's nothing I can do to help.

16:40.070 --> 16:41.730
Su Jian treated me like her older sister,

16:42.280 --> 16:43.370
yet I forgot her.

16:45.360 --> 16:46.420
Ji Ling took Wuyi away

16:46.430 --> 16:47.530
right in front of me,

16:48.550 --> 16:50.010
yet there was nothing I could do.

16:52.950 --> 16:53.890
Do you still think of her

16:54.880 --> 16:55.940
as your little sister?

16:56.190 --> 16:57.530
She is my little sister.

17:02.000 --> 17:03.250
Maybe I can't tell

17:03.250 --> 17:04.420
real memories from fake ones,

17:06.880 --> 17:08.570
but when Jiu Ying held me captive,

17:08.950 --> 17:10.010
it was Lu Wuyi

17:10.190 --> 17:11.290
who risked everything to save me.

17:11.400 --> 17:11.980
Wangyan...

17:13.470 --> 17:14.900
When she looked at me,

17:15.950 --> 17:17.010
the trust and dependence

17:17.840 --> 17:18.490
in her eyes

17:20.270 --> 17:21.460
couldn't have been fake.

17:22.710 --> 17:24.330
The one truly at fault in all this

17:24.670 --> 17:25.490
is Ji Ling.

17:26.120 --> 17:27.900
Wuyi was blinded by love.

17:28.270 --> 17:29.660
That's why she covered for him.

17:32.800 --> 17:33.770
You lied to me.

17:44.270 --> 17:45.090
Whatever the truth is,

17:46.120 --> 17:47.010
we have to find them first,

17:49.470 --> 17:50.770
not only to save Lu Wuyi,

17:51.470 --> 17:53.090
but also to put an end to this drought.

17:54.320 --> 17:55.180
I already have three strands

17:55.180 --> 17:56.570
of the Dragon Deity's Power in me.

17:56.990 --> 17:58.050
Once I get the last one,

17:58.710 --> 18:00.140
I can transform into a dragon and bring rain.

18:06.920 --> 18:08.140
I'll take you to Ji Ling.

18:09.560 --> 18:10.770
I know where he is.

18:13.710 --> 18:14.220
Why?

18:18.670 --> 18:20.140
Because I don't trust Lu Wuyi.

18:44.430 --> 18:44.980
Wu.

18:51.470 --> 18:52.980
Has the blowback from the rewinds gotten worse?

18:55.230 --> 18:55.980
That's none of your concern.

19:07.320 --> 19:07.810
Wu,

19:08.750 --> 19:09.940
we are alone now.

19:11.640 --> 19:12.490
Tell me.

19:13.030 --> 19:14.010
Why did you lie to me?

19:19.160 --> 19:21.140
Since you've lived through countless rewinds,

19:22.230 --> 19:23.570
you must've known Wu Shiguang and the others

19:23.710 --> 19:25.460
learned the truth from the painting,

19:27.190 --> 19:28.730
and that the pendant was no longer important.

19:30.400 --> 19:31.620
And you must've known long ago

19:32.320 --> 19:33.810
that there were no memories left inside it.

19:36.320 --> 19:36.770
Am I right?

19:38.430 --> 19:38.900
Yes.

19:48.470 --> 19:49.050
So

19:51.470 --> 19:52.810
from the very beginning,

19:53.880 --> 19:56.250
this was a trap you carefully laid for me.

19:58.560 --> 19:59.290
Then why did you

19:59.290 --> 20:00.730
trick me into stealing

20:02.230 --> 20:03.570
that pendant for you?

20:08.840 --> 20:10.900
Because you killed my sister.

20:25.320 --> 20:26.490
I killed Wu Wangyan?

20:31.360 --> 20:32.770
Do you know

20:34.800 --> 20:35.940
who matters most to me

20:37.880 --> 20:38.660
in this world?

20:46.800 --> 20:47.620
Wu Wangyan.

20:53.230 --> 20:53.900
That's right.

20:55.800 --> 20:56.750
Even after she learned

20:56.750 --> 20:58.330
that I was a monster created by Jiu Ying,

20:59.920 --> 21:01.660
that all my memories with her

21:02.160 --> 21:03.490
were fabricated,

21:07.430 --> 21:08.380
she still saw me

21:11.400 --> 21:13.460
as her irreplaceable little sister.

21:14.380 --> 21:18.020
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

21:18.460 --> 21:21.860
♪You always hang your head, saying nothing...♪

21:23.600 --> 21:24.140
Wuyi,

21:26.670 --> 21:28.140
don't call yourself a monster.

21:29.710 --> 21:30.360
Don't call yourself

21:30.360 --> 21:31.860
trash that nobody wants.

21:35.510 --> 21:37.050
I don't know what others

21:37.050 --> 21:37.860
can give you.

21:38.990 --> 21:40.050
But what I give you

21:41.470 --> 21:42.250
is my heart.

21:43.400 --> 21:44.220
You will always be

21:44.320 --> 21:45.490
my most beloved little sister.

21:46.100 --> 21:49.500
♪Great tree, O great tree...♪

21:50.670 --> 21:51.700
Those words

21:52.510 --> 21:53.980
were meant for Su Jian,

21:54.470 --> 21:55.730
not for me.

21:56.710 --> 21:57.420
This isn't real.

22:02.270 --> 22:03.090
Then what about this?

22:05.750 --> 22:06.810
Is this fake too?

22:08.470 --> 22:09.330
Listen to me carefully.

22:10.190 --> 22:11.010
I will

22:11.430 --> 22:12.900
say this to you once again.

22:14.840 --> 22:16.380
I will always be by your side.

22:17.140 --> 22:21.700
♪Great tree, O great tree♪

22:21.860 --> 22:25.620
♪Through snow and storm, you bend but breathe♪

22:25.900 --> 22:33.340
♪Let's set out toward the spring sunshine without fear♪

22:33.980 --> 22:37.660
♪Little grass, O little grass♪

22:37.940 --> 22:41.660
♪Rise on tiptoe, climb on bravely...♪

22:42.320 --> 22:43.460
You ruined her promise.

22:44.800 --> 22:45.660
You killed her.

22:46.640 --> 22:47.900
In all the previous rewinds,

22:50.160 --> 22:51.810
you killed her right in front of me.

22:53.700 --> 22:55.700
[First time]

23:02.400 --> 23:04.140
You joined forces with Jiu Ying.

23:05.030 --> 23:06.090
You killed Wangyan

23:06.920 --> 23:08.460
so Wu Shiguang would break down,

23:09.080 --> 23:10.490
giving Jiu Ying the chance

23:10.880 --> 23:12.330
to seize Wu Shiguang's body.

23:13.640 --> 23:14.770
You said I lied to you.

23:15.950 --> 23:16.490
You're right.

23:19.840 --> 23:20.730
I did lie to you.

23:21.950 --> 23:23.900
I was never trapped in the time rewinds.

23:24.950 --> 23:27.380
I chose to start over again and again

23:28.920 --> 23:30.140
so I could stop you.

23:31.920 --> 23:32.810
Too bad

23:33.270 --> 23:34.460
I failed every time.

23:35.470 --> 23:36.090
Wangyan!

23:40.140 --> 23:42.340
[Second rewind]

23:42.560 --> 23:43.050
Wangyan!

23:55.510 --> 23:56.140
- Wangyan! - Wuyi.

23:56.140 --> 23:56.990
[Third rewind]

23:56.990 --> 23:57.770
- What's wrong? - Wangyan,

23:57.990 --> 23:58.700
listen to me.

23:59.080 --> 23:59.900
Ji Ling is going to kill you.

24:00.080 --> 24:00.850
Come with me, now!

24:00.950 --> 24:01.490
Wuyi,

24:01.880 --> 24:02.660
what are you talking about?

24:02.750 --> 24:03.810
- I'm serious. - Nobody...

24:04.120 --> 24:04.620
Wang...

24:05.360 --> 24:06.290
Every single time,

24:06.670 --> 24:08.250
I had to watch my sister...

24:08.510 --> 24:09.050
Wangyan.

24:09.120 --> 24:10.250
...die by your hand.

24:12.030 --> 24:12.620
Wangyan!

24:13.320 --> 24:13.900
Wangyan!

24:13.900 --> 24:16.780
[Fifth rewind]

24:16.780 --> 24:18.230
[Sixth rewind]

24:18.230 --> 24:18.860
Wangyan.

24:20.100 --> 24:27.420
[Seventh rewind]

24:27.420 --> 24:29.980
[Eighth rewind]

24:29.980 --> 24:33.140
[Ninth rewind]

24:33.140 --> 24:35.020
[Tenth rewind]

24:35.020 --> 24:36.740
[Eleventh rewind]

24:36.740 --> 24:40.340
[Twelfth rewind]

24:41.270 --> 24:42.090
Ji Ling...

24:42.100 --> 24:43.860
[Thirteenth rewind]

24:44.270 --> 24:45.530
[Fourteenth rewind]
You killed my sister.

24:45.980 --> 24:47.030
[Fifteenth rewind]

24:47.030 --> 24:48.620
I'll never forgive you.

24:49.500 --> 24:51.540
[Sixteenth rewind]

24:52.080 --> 24:53.140
I hate you.

24:53.140 --> 24:54.820
[Seventeenth rewind]

24:55.190 --> 24:56.420
[Eighteenth rewind]
I hate you!

25:03.780 --> 25:06.180
[Nineteenth rewind]

25:12.080 --> 25:13.130
Again and again, I had to endure

25:13.130 --> 25:14.530
that piercing, bone-deep pain,

25:15.470 --> 25:17.010
and still I couldn't change a thing.

25:19.880 --> 25:20.770
But this time,

25:22.750 --> 25:23.620
I did it.

25:24.840 --> 25:25.860
Wu Shiguang didn't get

25:25.880 --> 25:27.220
the Dragon Deity's Power kept by Han Ba,

25:27.800 --> 25:29.420
and Wangyan learned what you were after.

25:30.270 --> 25:32.220
Everyone has seen your true colors.

25:37.470 --> 25:38.220
Wu,

25:40.470 --> 25:41.420
do you know

25:41.470 --> 25:43.180
why I trusted you so much?

25:44.510 --> 25:45.700
Do you know why

25:46.990 --> 25:48.490
I was willing to do everything you said?

25:52.230 --> 25:52.770
No.

25:55.360 --> 25:55.920
Because...

25:55.920 --> 25:56.770
I don't want to know.

26:07.320 --> 26:08.180
So Wu Wangyan

26:12.400 --> 26:13.660
is the only one you truly care about.

26:18.190 --> 26:19.220
Because she

26:21.360 --> 26:22.810
truly cares about me too.

26:22.950 --> 26:23.860
Don't I care about you?

26:37.470 --> 26:38.140
No matter.

26:39.750 --> 26:40.860
I've grown used to it by now.

26:41.750 --> 26:42.900
The people around me

26:43.840 --> 26:45.220
always end up

26:45.950 --> 26:46.620
leaving me

26:47.920 --> 26:48.940
one by one.

26:51.600 --> 26:52.460
No one ever stays.

26:54.670 --> 26:56.380
Lift the Word Magic from Mu Long.

26:59.400 --> 27:00.290
Even if I die,

27:02.950 --> 27:04.770
I won't undo the Word Magic for you

27:05.640 --> 27:07.090
to let you get the Dragon Deity's Power.

27:11.820 --> 27:13.740
♪Through a thousand old dreams♪

27:16.180 --> 27:18.220
♪Through a thousand shadows♪

27:26.820 --> 27:29.300
♪Don't be sad♪

27:29.300 --> 27:31.020
♪Through every yesterday♪

27:31.100 --> 27:33.620
♪Don't you cry♪

27:33.620 --> 27:35.500
♪Through every memory♪

27:35.580 --> 27:43.020
♪I'll always stay with you♪

27:44.180 --> 27:48.060
♪Like sand slipping through fingers tight♪

27:48.620 --> 27:52.500
♪Your name's the words I long to say♪

27:52.900 --> 27:56.540
♪I call for you, my only one♪

27:57.060 --> 28:04.260
♪You're my everlasting bloom♪

28:18.080 --> 28:19.180
You knew I was here?

28:21.080 --> 28:22.220
Have you forgotten

28:22.880 --> 28:24.010
how I found you in the first place?

28:25.360 --> 28:27.460
Why did you appear outside the Shilin Sect?

28:27.880 --> 28:28.770
I don't know.

28:29.510 --> 28:30.660
I just felt

28:31.230 --> 28:32.900
a voice calling me,

28:33.920 --> 28:35.050
telling me to come here.

28:35.990 --> 28:37.420
All these years later,

28:38.800 --> 28:40.490
that obsession is still in me,

28:43.120 --> 28:43.980
telling me to go find you.

28:45.880 --> 28:47.140
And somehow, I always do.

28:48.710 --> 28:50.090
I wonder if I'll ever be able

28:52.470 --> 28:53.180
to figure out

28:53.190 --> 28:54.420
where that obsession comes from.

28:55.750 --> 28:56.290
Li Jie,

28:57.800 --> 28:58.700
do you blame me

29:00.120 --> 29:01.220
for lying even to you?

29:07.080 --> 29:08.030
Though I don't know

29:08.030 --> 29:09.570
your true intentions,

29:10.510 --> 29:11.460
I have

29:13.030 --> 29:13.660
always known

29:13.660 --> 29:14.730
what kind of person you are.

29:16.120 --> 29:16.860
In all the years

29:17.600 --> 29:18.980
I've stayed by your side,

29:19.880 --> 29:20.730
a lot of the time,

29:21.230 --> 29:23.050
I didn't understand

29:23.560 --> 29:24.700
your choices or intentions.

29:25.920 --> 29:26.770
But I knew

29:29.360 --> 29:31.250
you must've had reasons you couldn't speak of.

29:32.470 --> 29:33.460
I will always be

29:34.160 --> 29:36.660
your shield and your blade.

29:39.360 --> 29:40.460
What do we do now?

29:42.750 --> 29:43.700
They're now

29:43.920 --> 29:44.980
all wary of me.

29:46.360 --> 29:48.050
Bring Mu Long here for me.

29:48.950 --> 29:49.940
I'll find a way

29:50.430 --> 29:51.940
to make Lu Wuyi lift the Word Magic.

29:54.880 --> 29:55.290
Understood.

29:58.080 --> 29:59.090
Be careful.

30:23.400 --> 30:24.700
Give me back my sister!

30:37.400 --> 30:38.660
You're using the Dragon Deity's Power

30:38.670 --> 30:39.420
against me?

30:39.800 --> 30:40.700
I'll go rescue Wuyi.

30:48.510 --> 30:49.660
You're trying to take my ring?

30:50.400 --> 30:52.220
I'm going to use Xiaowei's power inside that ring

30:52.560 --> 30:54.010
to lift the Word Magic on Mu Long.

30:55.120 --> 30:56.730
Like the Twelve Thoughts, the Spirit-Binding Ring

30:57.360 --> 30:57.980
obeys only its master.

30:59.640 --> 31:00.730
Even if you take it, it won't obey you.

31:01.640 --> 31:02.250
Its master?

31:03.470 --> 31:04.940
The ring's true master is Chi Wen,

31:05.670 --> 31:06.250
not you.

31:07.360 --> 31:08.860
The Dragon Deity's Power in me

31:09.120 --> 31:10.380
came from my brother.

31:10.840 --> 31:12.220
I'd like to see if it'll

31:12.950 --> 31:13.660
obey you

31:14.320 --> 31:15.090
over me!

31:22.400 --> 31:23.330
Ji Ling...

31:37.840 --> 31:38.460
Wangyan.

32:23.750 --> 32:24.620
Do you still

32:27.990 --> 32:29.460
see me as your little sister?

32:41.080 --> 32:42.330
No matter what happens,

32:44.640 --> 32:46.940
you will always be my most beloved little sister.

32:48.880 --> 32:49.620
I will

32:52.270 --> 32:53.810
always be by your side.

33:00.270 --> 33:01.860
The Word Magic was cast by Lu Wuyi.

33:02.640 --> 33:03.900
Even if you take the ring, it won't help.

33:04.560 --> 33:05.220
Don't believe him!

33:09.360 --> 33:10.380
Wangyan's Word Magic

33:10.400 --> 33:11.380
is far stronger than mine.

33:11.560 --> 33:13.090
If I had really cast it,

33:13.400 --> 33:14.810
how could she possibly fail to undo it?

33:15.920 --> 33:16.530
Wu Shiguang,

33:17.270 --> 33:18.420
Lu Wuyi somehow gained

33:18.430 --> 33:19.940
the power to rewind time.

33:20.360 --> 33:21.460
Her power

33:21.880 --> 33:23.460
has already surpassed all of ours.

33:23.840 --> 33:24.770
You're sharp enough.

33:25.880 --> 33:26.920
Haven't you noticed

33:26.920 --> 33:27.980
anything strange about her?

33:35.190 --> 33:36.980
I don't know which of you is telling the truth.

33:37.920 --> 33:38.730
But it doesn't matter.

33:39.400 --> 33:40.770
Once I get the Spirit-Binding Ring,

33:41.320 --> 33:42.250
I'll know.

33:59.840 --> 34:00.420
Wangyan,

34:07.270 --> 34:07.940
let's go.

34:56.200 --> 34:57.090
Master Dragon Deity...

35:00.920 --> 35:01.460
You Chi!

35:08.360 --> 35:09.380
Hand over the ring,

35:10.320 --> 35:11.530
or I'll kill him.

35:20.590 --> 35:23.300
Only the ancient divine jade, the Spirit-Storing Jade,

35:23.430 --> 35:24.860
can hold the Dragon Deity's Power.

35:25.510 --> 35:28.090
The Spirit-Storing Jade was split in two by heavenly fire.

35:28.510 --> 35:29.170
One became

35:29.590 --> 35:31.170
the six-eyed butterfly demon's

35:31.200 --> 35:31.940
Spirit-Storing Butterfly.

35:32.760 --> 35:33.530
The other became

35:33.990 --> 35:36.570
the Spirit-Binding Ring worn by the Dragon Deity.

35:45.280 --> 35:45.860
Wuyi!

35:49.760 --> 35:50.900
So it really was Lu Wuyi.

35:53.630 --> 35:54.210
Return.

36:01.880 --> 36:02.740
The Spirit-Binding Ring

36:04.360 --> 36:05.490
refused my summons.

36:06.280 --> 36:07.170
How is that possible?

36:08.470 --> 36:09.260
The ring

36:11.110 --> 36:12.380
has accepted Lu Wuyi as its master.

36:29.990 --> 36:31.460
Where could she have taken Long?

36:34.200 --> 36:35.030
What Lu Wuyi wants

36:35.030 --> 36:36.260
has always been the Dragon Deity's Power.

36:36.760 --> 36:37.530
Han Ba said...

36:37.920 --> 36:39.260
I hid the Dragon Deity's Power

36:40.840 --> 36:41.860
in the place where I

36:41.880 --> 36:42.820
first met Su Jian.

36:46.990 --> 36:47.940
The Wei mansion's weaving workshop.

36:56.880 --> 36:57.300
I...

36:58.070 --> 36:59.460
I want to go home.

37:00.680 --> 37:01.300
Don't be afraid.

37:05.320 --> 37:06.570
You'll be home soon.

37:08.760 --> 37:09.460
The Wei mansion?

37:09.950 --> 37:11.340
Isn't that just an ordinary household?

37:11.470 --> 37:12.900
How could it possibly hide the Dragon Deity's Power?

37:13.280 --> 37:15.050
The giant axle in the workshop

37:15.360 --> 37:16.690
is the core of a Firefluff Tree.

37:17.110 --> 37:19.090
I noticed it the first time I went to the Wei mansion.

37:19.400 --> 37:20.610
Back then, I wondered

37:20.840 --> 37:21.650
why Xiaowei always fled

37:21.720 --> 37:22.860
to the weaving workshop

37:23.200 --> 37:24.260
to escape the Ice Curse.

37:27.280 --> 37:28.530
The Firefluff Tree is of fire.

37:29.110 --> 37:30.740
The Ice Curse can't get close to it.

37:31.840 --> 37:34.030
Han Ba hid the Dragon Deity's Power inside the tree core

37:34.030 --> 37:35.170
and cultivated there

37:35.320 --> 37:36.780
to keep his demonic energy from leaking.

37:37.590 --> 37:38.860
What's a Firefluff Tree?

37:39.280 --> 37:40.380
It sounds pretty incredible.

37:40.800 --> 37:41.820
In remote antiquity,

37:41.920 --> 37:42.820
heaven and earth split apart.

37:43.470 --> 37:45.420
Nuwa sought five-colored stones to mend the sky

37:45.430 --> 37:47.490
and sent the Fox Queen to keep the earth together with four pillars of ice.

37:47.680 --> 37:48.980
Where the Four Ice Pillars stood

37:49.320 --> 37:51.820
grew four divine trees of metal, earth, water, and fire.

37:52.070 --> 37:53.980
The Firefluff Tree was one of them.

37:57.030 --> 37:57.820
Han Ba said

37:58.920 --> 38:00.130
that as soon as Mu Long woke up,

38:01.720 --> 38:02.650
the seal would undo itself.

38:04.590 --> 38:05.050
Oh, no.

38:05.880 --> 38:06.380
Let's go!

38:19.550 --> 38:21.050
Wake up.

38:29.430 --> 38:30.380
Wuyi,

38:31.920 --> 38:33.300
where... where am I?

38:34.070 --> 38:35.090
Where's Mr. Yan?

39:01.280 --> 39:01.860
Kneel.

39:50.280 --> 39:51.170
Drink it.

40:03.280 --> 40:04.130
I know him!

40:04.760 --> 40:06.170
I've seen him at the Dragon Deity Temple!

40:06.550 --> 40:07.650
He's Master Chi Wen!

40:08.150 --> 40:09.690
The Dragon Deity has answered our prayers!

40:10.030 --> 40:11.210
We're saved!

40:11.800 --> 40:13.280
Master Chi Wen!

40:13.280 --> 40:14.030
Master Chi Wen,

40:14.030 --> 40:15.020
please send us rain!

40:15.020 --> 40:15.740
Master Chi Wen,

40:15.800 --> 40:16.860
save us!

40:16.990 --> 40:18.640
You can't just stand by and watch us die!

40:18.640 --> 40:19.780
Master Chi Wen!

40:20.920 --> 40:21.820
Master Chi Wen!

40:23.150 --> 40:24.050
He's not the Dragon Deity.

40:24.110 --> 40:25.650
- He can't help us! - Master Chi Wen...

40:28.030 --> 40:28.860
He's not the Dragon Deity!

40:29.280 --> 40:30.340
He's a fake!

40:30.720 --> 40:31.820
He's a fraud!

40:32.200 --> 40:33.260
You're a fraud!

40:33.630 --> 40:35.420
Why did you lie to us?

40:42.950 --> 40:44.490
Why?

40:47.880 --> 40:48.860
Why can't I

40:48.880 --> 40:50.130
change the ending

40:51.200 --> 40:53.940
after everything I've done?

41:05.320 --> 41:05.980
Why?

41:54.110 --> 41:54.940
Why?

41:56.110 --> 41:57.090
Why?

42:10.510 --> 42:11.260
Ji Ling.

42:12.150 --> 42:12.980
Ji Ling.

42:14.110 --> 42:15.650
Ji Ling, wake up.

42:17.360 --> 42:18.340
Ji Ling.

43:04.620 --> 43:05.780
♪It's your light♪

43:05.980 --> 43:07.860
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:08.020 --> 43:11.140
♪That set the night alight♪

43:11.500 --> 43:18.020
♪And lead me through the fight♪

43:19.780 --> 43:21.660
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

43:22.100 --> 43:26.540
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

43:27.340 --> 43:29.020
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

43:29.180 --> 43:34.580
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:35.340 --> 43:40.740
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:43.060 --> 43:49.100
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:50.060 --> 43:52.220
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:52.500 --> 43:57.340
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:57.700 --> 44:00.020
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

44:00.220 --> 44:05.300
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

44:05.540 --> 44:07.540
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

44:07.820 --> 44:12.180
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

44:13.180 --> 44:20.140
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:36.700 --> 44:39.660
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:40.740 --> 44:44.140
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:44.940 --> 44:47.460
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:47.700 --> 44:50.780
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:51.180 --> 44:53.500
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:54.020 --> 44:58.420
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:58.660 --> 45:00.820
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

45:01.220 --> 45:06.180
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

45:06.420 --> 45:07.580
♪It's your light♪

45:07.780 --> 45:09.620
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:09.820 --> 45:12.940
♪That set the night alight♪

45:13.700 --> 45:23.140
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
